This paper discusses the measurement of visualization techniques, which is a topic that falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper covers various types of measures used in visualization, including perceptual characteristics (cs.GR), economic factors (cs.SI), and quantitative/qualitative measures (cs.CV, cs.MM). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely to be associated with this paper.
